WEBVTT

00:00.239 --> 00:04.118
You can catch the latest blockbuster movie here, playing twenty-four seven.

00:04.612 --> 00:06.171
Oh, and it's free.

00:06.354 --> 00:10.497
It's home to the country's tallest indoor slide, and it's not just for kids.

00:18.778 --> 00:21.993
Take a dip in the world's only airport outdoor pool.

00:22.819 --> 00:27.319
You can come here and see nearly 1,000 butterflies and over 40 species.

00:31.011 --> 00:34.032
Watch planes land and take off in the restroom.

00:34.587 --> 00:37.170
You can enjoy a free express hand massage.

00:38.109 --> 00:40.645
Take a seat for a free fragrance consultation.

00:44.344 --> 00:48.383
Take a nap in this public area, which is also known as the Snooze Lounge,...

00:48.591 --> 00:51.119
...and surrounded by the Sanctuary Garden.

00:52.711 --> 00:57.380
Oh, and also, Changi has been voted the world's best airport to sleep.

